I abandoned my family to play this game. Install at your own risk, but be prepared to forfeit your life for about a week. Tips for beginners: if it is telling you to create an event but you can't, look for the tiniest little icon near the store's register that looks like the icon for the event you had selected. You may have already placed it there by double tapping. Elevators are placed in a complete vertical row, so if elevators do not touch eachother, they will not work.
